The Finisher

A large drinking vessel is placed in the center of the table.
Players take turns doing the following:

    - Pour however much beer you would like to bet into the pitcher (max 1 Beer).
    - Another player holds a playing card so that you cannot see it. The player guesses black or red.
        If correct they pass the next pitcher to the next player and get 1pt. If Incorrect the player chugs the pitcher or Forfits!
    
    Winner is the last one standing.
    *If the last standing player wants to continue to gather more points they must bet a full beer each turn!
    *Should be played only as the last game!